quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,154,"Ni ngasim'bechetaga pa kwamba ya ŵandu ŵaakuwulajidwa petala lya Allah kuti: “Ŵawe.” Nambo ŵachijumi gamba kuti ngankupata kumanyilila."
  2,155,"Soni chitun'dinje ni chindu chakogoya (mpela ngondo), kwisa soni sala, kunandipa kwa ipanje, kwasika kwa maumi ni konasika kwa isogosi, ni mwatagulilani ŵakupilila abali jakusengwasya."
  2,156,"Aŵala ŵanti naga ipato yapatilemo akasatiji: “Chisimu uwwe ŵa Allah, soni chisimu uwwe Kukwakwe tuuchiujila.”"
  3,94,"Sano juchansepele Allah unami panyuma pa yalakweyi, basi ŵanganyao niŵachaŵe ŵakulitenda lupuso."
  3,95,"Jilani: “Allah aŵechete yakuona, basi kuyani dini ja Ibrahima jwakongoka soni nganaŵa mwa akuwanganya (Allah ni isanamu).”"
  3,96,"Chisimu naga nyumba jandanda jajaŵichidwe kwa ŵandu (kuŵa jagalagatilamo Allah) ni jajili pa Bakkah   (ku Maaka), jaupile soni (jiŵele) chongolo ku iwumbe yosope (ŵandu ni majini).",1:[Liloŵe lyakuti (Bakkah) likwamba malo gasyesyene galitaŵidwepo Likaaba ku Maaka.]
  4,34,"Achalume niŵali ŵakwajimila achakongwe (ŵalume ni ntwe weŵasa), ligongo lyanti Allah ŵachimbichisye ŵane mwa jamanjao kwapunda ŵane (achalume kwapunda achakongwe), soni ligongo lya chipanje chao chaakuŵa ali nkutola. Sano achimmasyeto ŵambone niŵali ŵakumanya, ŵakuligosa (yilu yao nigosa yipanje yaliŵasa) atamuno achiŵammakwao pali pangali, ligongo lyanti Allah ŵagosile (achimmasyetowo kupitila mwa achiŵammakwao ŵaakwapaga yaakulajila). Sano aŵala (achimmasyeto) ŵankukujogopa kuliikwesya kwao basi mwajamukani, (naga ngaakupikana) mwawunduchilani pagona, (naga kuunduka ngakukamuchisya) mwaputani (kwangaulasya), sano naga ali nkumpikanila, basi ngasimwasosela matala (gakwalagachisya). Chisimu Allah ni jwaali Jwapenani kusyene, Jwankulungwa nnope."
  4,35,"Sano naga (jenumanja akwiilanya) nkuujogopa ukangani wauli chilikati chao (ŵalume ni ŵankwao), basi tumisyani namangoswe jwakuchilume ni namangoswe jwakuchikongwe (kuti akachengulanye), naga ŵanaŵaŵiliwo ali asachile kwilanya, Allah tiŵakombolasye, chisimu Allah aŵele Jwakumanyilila nnope, Jwaasimanya abali syosope."
  4,36,"Soni mun'galagatilani Allah ni nkam'bwanganyaga ni chilichose, nombe achinangolo ŵanaŵaŵili mwatendelani yambone, kwisa soni ŵaulongo, ŵawina, masikini, jwakuŵandikana najo nyumba niali jwaulongo, jwakuŵandikana najo nyumba niali mundu nsape, n'jenu jwakutama najo imo, jwapaulendo ni (mateeka) gagapatile magasa genu gakun'dyo. Chisimu Allah ngakasaŵanonyela aŵala ŵali ŵakulikwesya ni kuliiti."